{"tid":629252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國稱空襲敘利亞命中所有目標　特朗普指行動完美執行","createTime":"2018-04-14T14:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T20:27:45.000Z","uid":147314,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6133024dfbb9176b81e4f1be32ee0f0731c7c307","tid":629252,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:06:19.000Z","msg":"美國稱空襲敘利亞命中所有目標　特朗普指行動完美執行<br />\n2018-04-14 HKT 21:50<br />\n<br />\n美國聯同英、法兩國，對敘利亞採取軍事行動，出動戰機及巡航導彈，攻擊當地化武設施。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部說，空襲規模比去年美國以近60枚導彈，轟炸敘利亞時大一倍，命中所有預定目標，敘利亞無任何武器，起到任何作用。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普說行動「完美執行」，形容是以正義力量，對抗野蠻及殘暴。英國首相文翠珊說，動武以外，別無選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391201-20180414.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391201-20180414.htm&d=B00LNoCgMr4boGkBCs%2BB%2BTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=44a9086c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391201-20180414.htm&h=9cc03360\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391201-20180414.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b72e22f892fbdc4c273c546efe13b1a985d62cf5","tid":629252,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:07:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/985130802668294144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F985130802668294144&d=B00LNoCgMr4boGkBCs%2BB%2BTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=be9bae13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F985130802668294144&h=d29e2afc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/985130802668294144</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">A perfectly executed strike last night.</span> Thank you to France and the United Kingdom for their wisdom and the power of their fine Military. <span style=\"color: red;\">Could not have had a better result. Mission Accomplished!</span>"},{"pid":"c573b959376a8b1bc209ea4b2677eafa4a161eb1","tid":629252,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:08:19.000Z","msg":"The strikes <span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;successfully hit every target&quot;</span> and that the allies &quot;took every measure and caution&quot; to only hit the intended targets, White said Saturday morning."},{"pid":"5bb053478666161641fbd1d324d153e04f28e577","tid":629252,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c573b959376a8b1bc209ea4b2677eafa4a161eb1","tid":629252,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:08:19.000Z","msg":"The strikes <span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;successfully hit every target&quot;</span> and that the allies &quot;took every measure and caution&quot; to only hit the intended targets, White said Saturday morning."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2018/04/14/politics/trump-syria-strike/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-syria-strike%2Findex.html&d=B00LNoCgMr4boGkBCs%2BB%2BTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=98242f79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-syria-strike%2Findex.html&h=824e1fcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2018/04/14/politics/trump-syria-strike/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"d0e87791e1516ad878840744faf9bb6875554809","tid":629252,"uid":2054,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://d279m997dpfwgl.cloudfront.net/wp/2017/08/trumpthumbsweb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd279m997dpfwgl.cloudfront.net%2Fwp%2F2017%2F08%2Ftrumpthumbsweb.jpg&h=104c7c2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d5051adbf7fb2cf20bda558ce178014a52e2445","tid":629252,"uid":104699,"lik